==English==

===Etymology===
Directly from latin meaning the black body or substance.

===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''[[substantia]] [[nigra]]'''

# The name given to the [[dopaminergic]] nucleus in the tegmentum, which is naturally colored black.
# The nucleus which projects to the [[globus pallidus]], and the lateral prefrontal cortex.
# The nucleus which is damaged in the brain of Parkinson's and Parkinsonian patients.